Package neureka.calculus.backend.executions

Interface ExecutorFor<TargetDevice extends Device>

  • Type Parameters:
    TargetDevice - The Device type for which an implementation of this interface has been made.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CLExecutor, HostExecutor
    public interface ExecutorFor<TargetDevice extends Device>
    This interface describes the functionality of an implementation of an execution procedure for a specific Device (interface) instance and OperationTypeImplementation (interface) instance! An instance of this interface is then a component of an OperationTypeImplementation instance which is itself a component of the OperationType class.
